---
import { liaHighlights, liaMeta, liaQuestions } from '../../data/site';
---

<section id="lia" class="section-space relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="orb -left-10 top-10 h-56 w-56 bg-sky-soft/18 animate-float-slow"></div>
  <div class="orb right-0 top-24 h-52 w-52 bg-rose-soft/18 animate-float"></div>
  <div class="section-curve"></div>

  <div class="shell relative z-10">
    <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1.1fr)_minmax(300px,0.9fr)] lg:items-center">
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div data-reveal style="--delay: 120ms" class="reveal-ready space-y-5">
          <span class="eyebrow">{liaMeta.badge}</span>
          <h2 class="section-heading max-w-4xl">{liaMeta.headline}</h2>
          <p class="section-copy max-w-2xl">
            {liaMeta.body}
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-ink-soft">
            {liaMeta.role}
          </p>
        </div>

        <div data-reveal style="--delay: 180ms" class="reveal-ready subsection-divider">
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <span class="subsection-kicker">O que a LIA pode fazer por você</span>
            <ul class="grid gap-4 text-base leading-8 text-ink-soft sm:grid-cols-2">
              {liaHighlights.map((item) => (
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3 rounded-[1.3rem] bg-white/80 px-4 py-4 shadow-[inset_0_0_0_1px_rgba(205,199,206,0.45)]">
                  <span class="mt-2 inline-flex h-2.5 w-2.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-rose to-sky"></span>
                  <span class="font-semibold">{item}</span>
                </li>
              ))}
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div data-reveal style="--delay: 360ms" class="reveal-ready glass-panel p-6 sm:p-7">
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 lg:flex-row lg:items-end lg:justify-between">
            <div>
              <span class="subsection-kicker">Perguntas rápidas</span>
              <div class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
                {liaQuestions.map((question) => (
                  <a
                    href={question.url}
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noreferrer"
                    class="inline-flex rounded-full bg-white px-4 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-ink shadow-soft ring-1 ring-mist transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:text-rose"
                  >
                    {question.label}
                  </a>
                ))}
              </div>
            </div>

            <a
              href={liaMeta.botUrl}
              target="_blank"
              rel="noreferrer"
              class="cta-primary shrink-0"
            >
              {liaMeta.ctaLabel}
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div data-reveal class="reveal-ready">
        <article class="surface-card relative overflow-hidden p-5 sm:p-6">
          <div class="absolute right-0 top-0 h-36 w-36 -translate-y-8 translate-x-8 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-rose-soft/25 to-sky-soft/25 blur-3xl"></div>
          <div class="relative space-y-4">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 rounded-full bg-ink px-4 py-2 text-[0.68rem] font-extrabold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-white">
              <span class="relative inline-flex h-3 w-3">
                <span class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full bg-sky animate-ping"></span>
                <span class="relative rounded-full bg-sky px-1"></span>
              </span>
              Assistente online agora
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-3 rounded-[1.8rem] bg-surface-low p-4">
              <div class="flex justify-end">
                <div class="max-w-[17rem] rounded-[1.4rem] rounded-br-md bg-gradient-to-r from-rose to-rose-soft px-4 py-3 text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-white">
                  Oi, LIA. Quero entender melhor se esse evento faz sentido para mim.
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-start">
                <div class="max-w-[18rem] rounded-[1.4rem] rounded-bl-md bg-white px-4 py-3 text-sm leading-6 text-ink shadow-soft ring-1 ring-mist">
                  Eu posso te ajudar com público, horário, local, ingresso e tudo o que está incluso
                  na experiência.
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-end">
                <div class="max-w-[16rem] rounded-[1.4rem] rounded-br-md bg-ink px-4 py-3 text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-white">
                  Perfeito. Me mostra por onde eu começo.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
